Yes, you do have to ask permission.

::Kluster::

Kluster watches K9 walk into the ship, turning his head to look at Eclipse. 
He starts to walk toward the bot, but then stops as he recieves Deemos' 
answer. Hostage? Knife-point? That didn't sound very Maximal-like.

"Allright," he replies, "Get back as soon as you can."

Kluster closes the link, walking to Eclipse. "News from Cybertron? What type 
of news?"
